data.description: Priced Below Market Value! Experience luxury living in this 3,656 sqft all-brick home with a walkout basement, situated on a spacious lot with a oversized 1168 sqft 3 car garage! Enter onto gleaming hardwood floors that guide you through open living spaces, seamlessly connecting each room. Interior expansion/attic could be finished to add additional square footage for an additional large rec area,man cave, or whatever your heart desires! The gourmet kitchen, featuring granite counters and stainless steel appliances, is a culinary haven. This home offers 5 bedrooms 3 on the main level and 2 in the finished basement rec area! The master suite provides a spa-like retreat with a huge en-suite and oversized walk in closet. The walkout basement and covered deck opens to the lush backyard, creating a versatile space for relaxation or entertaining. The large lot invites outdoor activities, complemented by a concrete circular driveway for a grand entrance. Welcome home!
